My project name : NonStopable chat
Type of project : omnichannel messaging and communication platform
PURPOSE:
    NonStopable chat is there to allow user to send and receive message across multiple communication platform 
    (WhatsApp,Messenger,Instagram,etc) while using single dashboard
PROBLEM STATEMENT WILL SOLVE:
        People use many messaging apps:
                  .whatsapp
                  .instagram
                  .facebook
        Bussiness struggle to:
                    .Reply fast
                    .manage many platform
                    .track customer
                    .Automate res
SOLUTION:
      NonStopable chat come as solution to solve those problem above,therefore 
     I will connect all messaging APIs into unified dashboard
     USERS:
         login once
         .connect to all account

FEATURES:
     1.User registration
     2.User login
     3.Messaging board
     4.search board
     5.notification board
     6.home page
     7.profile board
     8.more board
  TECHNOLOGY:
        FRONTEND:
             .React(vite)
             .css for styling
        BACKEND:
              .Mongoose
              .Mongodb
              .Express
              .Node.js
            

